acr.name: ACRCloud [Syntec TV]
acr.comment: API does not require a credit card to register, it has paid plans but also has good free usage plans.

watson.name: International Business Machines Corporation [IBM]
watson.comment: API is trial, you can use it for free with limits, but it requires a credit card to register account.

deepai.name: DeepAI
deepai.comment: The API does not require a credit card to register, it has paid plans, but it also has good free plans, you can also try it using the trial key below.

google.comment: API is trial, you can use it for free with limits, but it requires a credit card to register account, but you can use the free key below.
